    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Can be applied to any bladed melee weapon (note: chainsaws and similar weapons are not counted as bladed for this purpose).</p><p>A compartment and components for allowing a blade to poison enemies it strikes. As an action, the compartment can be loaded with any drug or poison. The weapon's next 6 swings will be tainted with the chemical. When such an attack hits and deals damage through armor, the target must attempt to beat a Resist Drugs/Torture check (DV varies - usually 13 or 15, use Physical skill for mooks). On failure, they're immediately afflicted with the primary effect of that substance.</p><ul><li><p>If the effect is timed, the timer refreshes with each subsequent hit and is reduced by 75%.</p></li><li><p>Targets should roll for any secondary effects immediately, if the primary effect is applied.</p></li></ul>"
    },
